title: Mecca Ultimo
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Western, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A specialty coffee roaster who operates a cafe located on the fringe of the Sydney CBD. Offers coffee alongside a small, interesting food menu and a separate vegetarian/vegan/gluten free menu. Whole foods is the focus for dishes. Breakfast for vegans include granola with almond milk and coconut yogurt, chia pudding, green smoothies, sourdough toast with sides and a vegan shakshouka. Lunch for vegans is shakshouka. Almond milk and coconut yogurt made-in-house.
